          "Multiply numerators together and denominators together.",
          "\\(3\\times2=6\\) and \\(4\\times5=20\\).",
          "\\(\\frac{6}{20}=\\frac{3}{10}\\) in simplest form."
        ]
      },
      "worked_solution": "\\(\\frac{3}{4}\\times\\frac{2}{5}=\\frac{3\\times2}{4\\times5}=\\frac{6}{20}=\\frac{3}{10}\\)."
